		<h4>Reward - The Singing Short Sword!</h4>
You are almost there. To get your singing short sword give following items to Baldric Slezaf back in the Dreadlands: 
<ol>
<li>Top of page 24 
<li>Bottom of page 24 
<li>Page 25 
<li>Mystical lute from Foplar 
</ol>
		He will reward you with the Singing Short Sword!<br><br>
